Dileep arrested in Malayalam actress abduction case.
Shocking details continue to emerge in the Malayalam actress abduction case. Actor Dileep has now been arrested in connection with the case.Dileep's name got linked to the case after prime accused Pulsar Suni said in a statement to the police that he wrote a letter to the actor. Dileep denied knowing Pulsar Suni, but a selfie leaked to the media showed the accused on the sets of the actor's film Georgettan's Pooram.The actor was interrogated along with director Nadirshah for 13 hours to understand his involvement in the case, and his wife Kavya Madhavan's place of business was raided as well.